## Architecture Context

### Parent BOM

All services inherit from a **custom Citi parent BOM** (not standard Spring Boot parent):

```xml
<parent>
    <groupId>com.citi.169073.ccp.rel</groupId>
    <artifactId>ccp-spring-boot-starter-parent-master</artifactId>
    <version>2026.6.13.RELEASE</version>  <!-- or 2026.4.20.RELEASE -->
</parent>
```

**Critical:** This parent BOM respects standard Spring Boot version property names.
Setting `<spring-framework.version>` in `<properties>` overrides all transitive
Spring Framework dependencies at build time.

